  "prompt": "An ancient scroll divided into three interwoven panels. The first panel shows young sovereign children waking from vivid dreams, surrounded by symbols of flame, keys, and crossroads cities (Istanbul, Johannesburg, Montreal, Santiago, Kyoto). The second panel shows sand guardians rising from cracked desert stone in Sinai, Atacama, and Moab, with swirling wind and salt glyphs around them. The third panel shows broken mirrors and digital reflections fading into shadow, with glowing sigils revealing hidden truths. The scroll glows faintly with mythic light, and the numbers 3:33 are carved at the top, surrounded by flame motifs.",
